name: Delta A350 Inaugural
description:
EDIT: The A350 uses Rolls Royce engines, not Pratt & Whitneys.

Delta *finally* launches a true First Class. Join me as I fly from Detroit to Tokyo in Seat 2D on Delta's first ever revenue flight of their brand new $300 million dollar A350!

Please "Like," "Comment," and "Subscribe!"

Check out my travel blog: https://greenergrass.com/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jebbrooks/

Music is "Cristaux" by Andr√© Aguado and "Sad Drama 15" by Merlean
